				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Having &quot;empty&quot; space in your OAM is not a problem at all. As long as they are at an offscreen location they won't interfere with your other sprite rendering. It will not help efficiency to compact this space (probably the opposite, since it may take you more time to compact it). I wouldn't bother trying to do this until/unless you run out of space and want to have more sprites.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

